{"tid":1576041,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［求舉報］呢排好多二手名牌假貨 包括CÉLINE, ysl, loewe,balenciaga, LV, Dior","createTime":"2019-09-17T05:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:23:42.000Z","uid":88962,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfba2e2ce18132ced35fcd4eb4eacd3d4673393","tid":1576041,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"我見好多賣二手名牌既ig shop 都post左個聯合聲明話某d ig shop ，尤其係係Carousell 有post既某d shop ,賣緊啲超高仿 . 好多人中招。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢地既聯合聲明cap圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDHD0pT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDHD0pT.png&h=0b938ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網買二手實係有風險既，好多人都會要求賣家陪驗。但今次有唔少中招既買家都係有揾佢地陪驗左ok先買。<br />\n有留意開既巴絲都知有間係旺角銀行中心好出名會收錢幫人驗袋既二手鋪 。未知係因為啲貨真係超高仿所以佢地驗唔到？有冇扯貓尾情況我評論唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登巴絲係咪係度可自發係度舉報番有問題既shop,等少啲人中招?<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前連登講過bxholic 既post有篤左啲賣假野既ig shop出黎，但希望大家可以響度集體討論吓, post之前cap圖同埋講番覺得佢地賣假野既原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： C&Eacute;LINE fans, 唔係CELINE fan<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以依家淨係可以買二手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ebfab8bf8d63bf1a44c3e48376d785994ea5f5","tid":1576041,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f706951f2068eadc5893cc7bd2d609c03507275","tid":1576041,"uid":38494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/as