假袋唔收寄賣。然後我越睇越多野 我就同luxury.luxhk講話如果佢都有懷疑賣過假既寄賣野比人 要揾番其他發聲明店主 一齊去聲討果個所謂彭小姐。然後我講完無幾耐 再番去search佢個ig 就彈左user not found出黎 佢驚到自己delete左個ig 我都算執番身彩啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未delete account 前ig</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZoozA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZoozA5.jpg&h=d435c570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>賣買對話</strong></span></span><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFZGmf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFZGmf5.jpg&h=61c16168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPRaeA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPRaeA5.jpg&h=1083cf2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>講完無耐即刻驚到delete左account</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yeMdWPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyeMdWPq.jpg&h=05fa8f7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85f7ed702f0b2442feea330e9eb61a8439bd4465","tid":1576041,"uid":94958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"香港仲有冇可靠既驗袋鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03742edd353c4b750595e726c44453b3ef6f3d23","tid":1576041,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f7ed702f0b2442feea330e9eb61a8439bd4465","tid":1576041,"uid":94958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"香港仲有冇可靠既驗袋鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"聽聞揭發件事既人 係係大陸揾到專業既鑑定師 比錢佢鑑定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你可以話大陸唔可信 但係事主問人拎左個係專門店買既真袋黎對比 佢買到果個假既真係差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkg